  "body": "# Problem\r\nSee also #11821 \r\n\r\nCurrently, following #11723 the account balance is not automatically updated for newly generated accounts and imported accounts with zero value. The user can pull to refresh to start fetching balance. However, pull to refresh is currently only available on individual account screens, not on the account overview screen. \r\n\r\nEspecially for users with only one account, this can be difficult to discover, resulting in the user not seeing updates or knowing how to update their balance after sending funds to their empty account.\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\ntbd\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\nPull to refresh is available on account overview screen\r\n\r\n## Future Steps\r\n#11821 ",
